### Makes slides 2.5x faster, to match a max level Snowdrift Artifact's slide speed. Infinite Slide mod is recommended.
### BE CAREFUL! This also affects forced slides, so YOU WILL DIE to Graveward's forced slide if you're not ready for it!

SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Operative/_Shared/_Design/Character/BPChar_Operative.Default__BPChar_Operative_C,Att_SlideSpeedMultiplier,0,,(Value=2.5,BaseValue=2.5)
SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Character/BPChar_Gunner.Default__BPChar_Gunner_C,Att_SlideSpeedMultiplier,0,,(Value=2.5,BaseValue=2.5)
SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Character/BPChar_Siren.Default__BPChar_Siren_C,Att_SlideSpeedMultiplier,0,,(Value=2.5,BaseValue=2.5)
SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Beastmaster/_Shared/_Design/Character/BPChar_Beastmaster.Default__BPChar_Beastmaster_C,Att_SlideSpeedMultiplier,0,,(Value=2.5,BaseValue=2.5)

###
### Name: Slide Jumper
### Version: 1.0.0
### Author: Po誰po誰
### Categories: cheat, joke
###
### License: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-SA 4.0)
### License URL: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/
###

### I felt jumping out of a fast slide felt disappointingly slow, so this makes jumps out of a slide faster and cover a longer distance, Titanfall/Apex Legends style.
### This is intended to be used with my Faster Slide mod or a high level Snowdrift artifact.

SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/_Shared/_Design/Sliding/SlidingData_Shared.SlidingData_Shared,JumpHorizontalSpeedScale,0,,6

## Fuel passively regenerates very quickly rather than depletes (just in case)
SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/_Shared/_Design/Pools/ResourcePool_IronBear_Duration.ResourcePool_IronBear_Duration,BaseConsumptionRate,0,,-100.0
SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/_Shared/_Design/Pools/ResourcePool_IronBear_Duration.ResourcePool_IronBear_Duration,BaseOnIdleRegenerationDelay,0,,0.0

